name: OceanWavesRadio
skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: ocean waves radio
des:
Here on Ocean Waves Radio will be your favorite station to hear everything from the 50’s to today. We offer many genres including rock, country, easy and smooth listening, alternative, Christian, talk and more. It has fun stuff for everyone! 
This skill will provide you a way to stream vinyl vibes and many solid shows from a variety of DJ styles. This skill will get to us much quicker and more efficiently. We want to make things simple for our listeners. 
You won’t miss out on anything, especially chances at a free gift. Who doesn’t like free? One of the best things is that your DJ’s and management team might just speak to you specifically. 
Can’t wait to hear what y’all think. Check it out!
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
